Revision history for Perl extension Lingua::Klingon::Recode.

1.02	Sun 2004-05-09
	- Test for "Q" vs. "q" (which doesn't work in the case of lossy
	  tlhingan hol / TLHINGAN HOL, of course)

1.01	Sun 2004-05-09
	- Parse "ngh" correctly in "tlhIngan Hol"; "monghom" is now
	  correctly m+o+n+gh+o+m rather than m+o+ng+(unrecognised letter
	  h, passed through)+o+m.
	- Update tests to test various "ng"/"ngH"/"ngh"/"nggh"
	  situations.

1.0	Sun 2003-10-19
	- original version

